<http://example.org/req/408#Proc_Repeated_Switch_Operation> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000003>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015>,
